# Project Demo Video

This folder contains the complete project demonstration video for the **AI-Enabled Student Admission System**, developed using **Salesforce Developer Edition**.

## Demo Video

**File:** `AI_Enabled_Student_Admission_System_Demo.mp4`

The video provides a complete walkthrough of the project, including the project idea, problem statement, Salesforce implementation, automation, AI capabilities, reporting, security, and overall system workflow.

## About the Project

The **AI-Enabled Student Admission System** is a Salesforce-based solution designed to improve and streamline student admission and enrolment management.

The system centralizes student, course, and enrolment information while using Salesforce automation and AI capabilities to reduce manual work, improve data accuracy, support admission-related decisions, and provide useful operational insights.

